Package: raschreg
Type: Package
Title: Item Response Theory models including explanatory variables of the ability parameter
Version: 1.0
Date: 2020-03-16
Author: person("Fernando", "Massa", email = "fmassa@iesta.edu.uy",
  role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID='https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2922-4097'))
Maintainer: Fernando Massa <fmassa@iesta.edu.uy>
Description: Provides a set of functions to estimate, simulate and visualize Item Response Theroy models such as: Rasch model, Rasch model with a common discrimination parameter and the Two Parameter Logistic model). Inclusion of regression effects of the ability paramters are allowed. Marginal log-likelihood is approximated using the Laplace method.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: cowplot, 
         ggplot2, 
         Rcpp,
         Rdpack,
         rlang
RdMacros: Rdpack
LinkingTo: Rcpp
